Class HeatControlSystem, SM sm, State house.room.room.noHeatReq.waitForHeat
From house.room.room.noHeatReq.waitForHeat to house.room.room.noHeatReq.idleNotHeat automatically Guard: [((setTemp - actualTemp) <= 2)]
From house.room.room.noHeatReq.waitForHeat to house.room.room.noHeatReq.waitForHeat automatically Guard: [waitedForWarm < WARMUPTIMER] Transition Action: setWaitedForWarm(waitedForWarm + 1);
Class HeatControlSystem, SM sm, State house.room.room.heatReq.idleHeat

From house.room.room.noHeatReq.waitForHeat to house.room.room.heatReq automatically Guard: [(waitedForWarm == WARMUPTIMER) && (valvePos == 2) && ((setTemp - actualTemp) > 2)] Transition Action: setRequestHeat(true);

start to house.room.room.heatReq.idleHeat
Class HeatControlSystem, SM sm, State house.room.room.heatReq.waitForCool

From house.room.room.heatReq.waitForCool to house.room.room.noHeatReq automatically Guard: [(valvePos == 0) && (COOLDOWNTIMER == waitedForCool) && ((actualTemp - setTemp) > 2)] Transition Action: setRequestHeat(false);
From house.room.room.heatReq.waitForCool to house.room.room.heatReq.idleHeat automatically Guard: [((actualTemp - setTemp) <= 2)]
From house.room.room.heatReq.waitForCool to house.room.room.heatReq.waitForCool automatically Guard: [waitedForCool < COOLDOWNTIMER] Transition Action: setWaitedForCool(waitedForCool + 1);

From furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceAct to furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceOff automatically Guard: [deactivate == true]

From furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceAct to furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceAct automatically Guard: [furnaceStartUpTime < FURNACETIMER] Transition Action: setFurnaceStartUpTime(furnaceStartUpTime + 1);
Class HeatControlSystem, SM sm, State furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceRun
From furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceAct to furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceRun automatically Guard: [furnaceStartUpTime == FURNACETIMER] Transition Action: setFurnaceRunning(true);
From furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceRun to furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal.furnaceOff automatically Guard: [deactivate == true]
From furnace.furnace.furnaceErr to furnace.furnace.furnaceNormal automatically Guard: [furnaceReset == true]
